{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Create a single-screen weather forecast application that displays the current weather at the selected location. The application will use free to use and publicly available API. Get the necessary data from the API and then present it. The following specification is describing the appearance and functionality of the application."}]},{"anchor":"Specification","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Specification"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The weather detail screen will display the current weather for current location. The screen also contains the weather forecast for the following days. The location can be added\/removed from favorites."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If the detail does not fit on the device screen, the top navigation will be displayed dynamically after scrolling down."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"assignment.png"}]},{"anchor":"Technical-requirements","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Technical requirements"},{"anchor":"Programming","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Programming"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Follow the basic principles of OOP"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Consistent and readable code"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift programming language"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"We recommend you to choose swift style guide"}]}]}]},{"anchor":"System-and-devices","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"System and devices"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"iOS 15 SDK"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"pa